        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Usage</strong> imbued into any weapon ikon</p><hr /><p>Your weapon has the might of legends, capable of shooting or striking any light out of the sky. The imbued ikon gains the following abilities.</p>\n<p><strong>Immanence</strong> (darkness) on a successful critical hit with the weapon, the weapon casts 2nd-rank darkness centered on the target of the attack.</p>\n<p><strong>Transcendenceâ€”Break the Sun's Legs</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">2</span> (cold, concentrate, darkness, transcendence) You make a slashing motion over the brightest source of light, whether it's a torch or the sun in the sky. A gash appears over the light source, visible to all, and devours the light. The entire area within a @Template[type:burst|distance:120] around you is affected by a 9th-rank darkness spell for 1 minute. The stolen light is channeled to your eyes, granting you greater darkvision for the duration of the effect.</p>"
